, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1be80b0a-b5a2-4898-a77d-4fd80df00a22_375x134.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1be80b0a-b5a2-4898-a77d-4fd80df00a22_375x134.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></figure></div><p>几天后，斯坦福大学的一位讲师在旨在解释和捍卫哈马斯袭击的课堂练习中将<a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/stanford-lecturer-suspended-after-allegedly-calling-israel-a-colonizer-in-class">犹太学生列为</a>“殖民者”：</p><blockquote><p>斯坦福大学的一名讲师已被停职，因为学校正在调查他在两堂课上根据学生的“身份和背景”针对学生的指控，他在两堂课上就<a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/keyword/israel">以色列</a>与<a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/keyword/hamas">哈马斯</a>冲突进行了即兴演讲。犹太学生领袖<em>努里亚·</em>科恩 (Nourya Cohen) 告诉《旧金山纪事报》，在其中一堂课上，讲师首先将战争归咎于犹太复国主义者，然后要求“犹太学生举手”。 “他问有多少犹太人在大屠杀中丧生，”科恩说，并补充说，当有人回答六百万时，“他说，‘是的。只有六百万。”一位自称在课堂上与三名学生交谈过的拉比告诉犹太新闻媒体<a href="https://forward.com/news/564587/stanford-university-jewish-students-instructor-hamas/">《前进》</a> ，讲师继续说道，“殖民者杀害了超过六百万人。以色列是一个殖民者。”科恩和另一位学生领袖声称，老师随后在班上四处将学生划分为“殖民者”或“被殖民者”，具体取决于他们所说的来自哪里。</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/yes-its-possible-to-imagine-progressive">阅读更多</a></p>;
Liberalism is losing the information warBecause it's refusing to fight. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/liberalism-is-losing-the-information https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/liberalism-is-losing-the-informationNoah Smith Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:08:13 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg" width="716" height="506.0732984293194" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:675,&quot;width&quot;:955,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:716,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12571d15-a867-4d57-8b2a-ca04752e5347_955x675.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p> <em>“将宣传理念注入大多数人的头脑中最简单的方法就是在他们没有意识到自己正在被宣传的情况下，让它通过娱乐图片的媒介传播。” ——埃尔默·戴维斯，战争信息办公室主任</em></p><p>上图来自一部名为<em>《Don&#39;t Be a Sucker》</em>的短片，该短片于 1943 年第二次世界大战最激烈时期首次上映，并于 1947 年战争结束后重新上映。这部电影描绘了一位本土主义、偏执的煽动者站在国旗前，自称是“<em>美国</em>美国人”，辱骂少数族裔。在影片中，一名观看该节目的男子（代表美国普通人）遇到了一名匈牙利难民，后者警告他纳粹在德国掌权的过程中存在反少数群体的恐慌。与此同时，影片的叙述者赞扬了美国的多样性和自由社会的内在力量。 <em>《别做傻瓜》</em>至今仍具有很大影响力，并在 2017 年夏洛茨维尔示威活动后<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/aug/14/dont-be-a-sucker-anti-nazi-film-charlottesville">作为反对法西斯主义的警告而广泛流传</a>。</p><p>如果您还没有看过，那么值得您花 22 分钟： </p><div id="youtube2-vGAqYNFQdZ4" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;vGAqYNFQdZ4&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/vGAqYNFQdZ4?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>这部电影是谁制作的？是一些反法西斯公民关心遏制国内本土主义浪潮并在国外反击轴心国吗？是一些非营利组织还是公民团体？没有。 2017年进步青年广泛分享的电影<em>《别傻了</em>》是由美国战争部制作和推广的。</p><p>这甚至不是罗斯福和杜鲁门政府用来说服美国人支持反法西斯主义斗争的唯一一部电影。另一个著名的例子是<em><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Why_We_Fight">《我们为何而战》</a></em> ，这是由当时著名导演弗兰克·卡普拉在第二次世界大战期间执导的一系列电影，向持怀疑态度的公众解释美国参战的原因。如果您愿意，您可以<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLqqqqZrD37h5e7dYRQa8Udia9bbx_Ig-w">在 YouTube 上观看整个系列</a>。我在高中时看过第一部分，我清楚地记得有一个图表描绘了轴心国如何对欧洲和亚洲不满意，并最终转向美国： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F09909f02-1a63-4723-9fc0-65bc721914ba_897x652.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F09909f02-1a63-4723-9fc0-65bc721914ba_897x652.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F09909f02-1a63-4723-9fc0-65bc721914ba_897x652.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fim