t one, but TWO episodes of <a href="https://link.chtbl.com/Econ102">Econ 102 with Erik Torenberg</a> this week. Here&#39;s a fairly dark and dire episode about the danger of World War 3 and the end of Pax Americana: </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8a989dc76846ca8ca068ddca77&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E15: Why Pax Americana is Dying and What Happens if China Attacks Taiwan&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/2Mmd4IubcxLV946z5PvtTQ&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/2Mmd4IubcxLV946z5PvtTQ" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p> Here are <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/e15-why-pax-americana-is-dying-and-what-happens-if/id1696419056?i=1000631790527">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b72fspwaOUU">YouTube</a> links in case you don&#39;t happen use Spotify.</p><p> And here&#39;s a fairly cheery and upbeat episode about techno-optimism: </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8aa2e60a8e34ce6b48a1073805&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E16: Techno-Optimism, Nuclear Energy, and How To Enable More Innovation&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/5GtFZ6ADPlVGKWYyKRrE1T&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/5GtFZ6ADPlVGKWYyKRrE1T" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p> Here are <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/be/podcast/e16-techno-optimism-nuclear-energy-an